trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> class represents a connection to a DSML Gateway using SOAP over HTTP.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> representa uma conexão a um Gateway de DSML usando SOAP sobre HTTP.

trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.#ctor(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlDirectoryIdentifier,System.Net.NetworkCredential,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType)" /> cria e inicializa uma nova instância de uma classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> usando o identificador, as credenciais de rede e o tipo de autenticação especificados.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="identifier" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="identifier" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="authType" /> value is not one of the DSML supported values.
trans-unit.target: O valor <paramref name="authType" /> não é um dos valores compatíveis do DSML.

trans-unit.source: DSML only supports Anonymous, Ntlm, Basic, Negotiate and digest.
trans-unit.target: O DSML dá suporte apenas a Ntlm, Basic, Negotiate e digest.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="authType" /> value is not one of the constants defined in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: O valor <paramref name="authType" /> não é uma das constantes definidas na enumeração <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" />.

trans-unit.target: Valor de demanda: <see cref="F:System.Security.Permissions.SecurityAction.Demand" />

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous request.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto derivado do <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> que faz referência à solicitação assíncrona.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Abort(System.IAsyncResult)" /> method cancels the asynchronous request.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Abort(System.IAsyncResult)" /> cancela a solicitação assíncrona.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> é nulo (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> was not returned by the corresponding call to <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="asyncResult" /> não foi retornado pela chamada correspondente para <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.AuthType" /> property contains one of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration that specifies the authentication type.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.AuthType" /> contém um dos valores da enumeração <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> que especifica o tipo de autenticação.

trans-unit.source: One of the values of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeration that specifies the authentication type.
trans-unit.target: Um dos valores de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AuthType" /> enumeração que especifica o tipo de autenticação.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to send.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> a ser enviado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" /> function.
trans-unit.target: A função <see cref="T:System.AsyncCallback" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that contains the state data for this request.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Object" /> que contém os dados de estado para essa solicitação.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> method begins asynchronously sending the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to the server.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" /> começa enviando assincronamente o objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> especificado para o servidor.

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that references the asynchronous send.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto derivado do <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> que faz referência ao envio assíncrono.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="request" /> é nulo (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> method instructs the DSML server to start a new session.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> instrui o servidor DSML para iniciar uma nova sessão.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O método será bloqueado enquanto aguarda uma resposta do servidor de DSML e atingirá o tempo limite de acordo com o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when a session is already open on the connection.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando uma sessão já está aberta na conexão.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the XML returned from the Server in response to the <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> is not well-formed.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando o XML retornado pelo servidor em resposta ao <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSession" /> não está bem formado.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server or when the server is out of available sessions.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando há uma falha de comunicação com o servidor DSML ou quando o servidor está fora das sessões disponíveis.

trans-unit.source: An object derived from <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> that contains state data for this request.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto derivado de <see cref="T:System.IAsyncResult" /> que contém os dados de estado para essa solicitação.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSendRequest(System.IAsyncResult)" /> method completes an asynchronous send request.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSendRequest(System.IAsyncResult)" /> conclui uma solicitação de envio assíncrono.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> object that contains the results of the request.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> que contém os resultados da solicitação.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when <paramref name="asyncResult" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Lançada quando <paramref name="asyncResult" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Thrown if <paramref name="asyncResult" /> was not returned by the current instance from a call to <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.
trans-unit.target: Lançada se <paramref name="asyncResult" /> não foi retornado pela instância atual de uma chamada para <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.BeginSendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument,System.AsyncCallback,System.Object)" />.

trans-unit.source: The request did not complete.
trans-unit.target: A solicitação não foi concluída.

trans-unit.source: No stream is available.
trans-unit.target: Nenhum fluxo está disponível.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the response returned by server is not valid.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando a resposta retornada pelo servidor não é válida.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when abort was previously called or when an error occurred while processing the request.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando a anulação foi chamada anteriormente ou quando ocorreu um erro ao processar a solicitação.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSession" /> method ends the session with the DSML server and clears the <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> property.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.EndSession" /> encerra a sessão com o servidor DSML e limpa a propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" />.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will time out according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O método será bloqueado enquanto aguarda uma resposta do servidor de DSML e atingirá o tempo limite de acordo com o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: If the DSML server has already terminated the session on its own, a <xref:System.Net.WebException> will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: Se o servidor DSML já finalizou a sessão por conta própria, um <xref:System.Net.WebException> será lançada.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> is still valid after the exception is thrown, the request never reached the server and the connection is still considered valid.
trans-unit.target: Se o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId%2A> ainda é válida após a exceção é gerada, a solicitação nunca atingiu o servidor e a conexão ainda é considerado válido.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando há uma falha de comunicação com o servidor DSML.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is no open session.
trans-unit.target: Gerada quando não há nenhuma sessão aberta.

trans-unit.source: Sends an object to the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: Envia um objeto para o servidor DSML.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> object that contains the request.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> que contém a solicitação.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest)" /> method sends a single <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest)" /> envia um único objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> object that contains the results of the request.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryResponse" /> que contém os resultados da solicitação.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="request" /> é nulo (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The DSML server returned an error response.
trans-unit.target: O servidor DSML retornou uma resposta de erro.

trans-unit.source: The operation returned a failure code.
trans-unit.target: A operação retornou um código de falha.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object sent to the server.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> enviado ao servidor.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument)" /> method sends a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> object to the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SendRequest(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument)" /> envia um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument" /> para o servidor DSML.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> object that contains the results of the request.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlResponseDocument" /> que contém os resultados da solicitação.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="request" /> is null (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="request" /> é nulo (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> property contains the active session ID.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SessionId" /> contém a ID de sessão ativa.

trans-unit.source: The active session ID.
trans-unit.target: A ID de sessão ativa.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SoapActionHeader" /> property contains the SOAP Action Header sent with other HTTP headers.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.SoapActionHeader" /> contém o cabeçalho de ação SOAP enviado com outros cabeçalhos HTTP.

trans-unit.source: The SOAP Action Header sent with other HTTP headers.
trans-unit.target: O cabeçalho de ação SOAP enviada com outros cabeçalhos HTTP.

trans-unit.source: The default value of this property is "#batchRequest".
trans-unit.target: O valor padrão dessa propriedade é "#batchRequest".

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Timeout" /> property contains the length of time, in seconds, before the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> times out.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection.Timeout" /> contém o período, em segundos, antes que o <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> atinja o tempo limite.

trans-unit.source: The length of time, in seconds, before the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> times out.
trans-unit.target: O período, em segundos, antes que o <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapHttpConnection" /> atinja o tempo limite.
